<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Thank You</title>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=10">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">  

    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
            color: #ffffff;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            animation: fadeInDown 2s ease-in-out;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 2s ease-in-out;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .thank-you {
            margin-top: 20px;
            animation: bounceIn 2s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0%, 20%, 40%, 60%, 80%, 100% {
                animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.610, 0.355, 1.000);
            }
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale3d(0.3, 0.3, 0.3);
            }
            20% {
                transform: scale3d(1.1, 1.1, 1.1);
            }
            40% {
                transform: scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 0.9);
            }
            60% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale3d(1.03, 1.03, 1.03);
            }
            80% {
                transform: scale3d(0.97, 0.97, 0.97);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale3d(1, 1, 1);
            }
        }

        .names {
            margin-top: 15px;
            animation: fadeIn 4s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .name {
            font-size: 23px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(#ff416c, #ff4b2b);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Muito obrigado!</h1>

    <div class="thank-you">
        <h2>Agradecimentos Especiais:</h2>
        <div class="names">
            <div class="name"><strong>iGust</strong> - iGust Team</div>
            <div class="name"><strong>aMathyzin</strong> - Grupo aMathyzin</div>
            <div class="name"><strong>Lion fé</strong> - Lion FPS</div>
            <div class="name"><strong>Gomes7Arts</strong> - GomesArts</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Seu nome não está aqui? Relaxa, no próximo painel com certeza vai estar.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
